### Terminal Value Calculation
| Terminal Value (Year 10) | =FCF_Year10 * (1 + Terminal_Growth) / (Discount_Rate - Terminal_Growth) |
| Present Value of Terminal Value | =Terminal_Value / (1 + Discount_Rate)^10 |
| **Total Enterprise Value** | =SUM(Present_Values) + PV_Terminal_Value |
| **NPV** | =Total_Enterprise_Value - Initial_Investment |

