### Black-Scholes Calculations
| Metric | Formula | Value |
|--------|---------|-------|
| d1 | =(LN(S/K)+(r-q+0.5*σ²)*T)/(σ*SQRT(T)) | |
| d2 | =d1-σ*SQRT(T) | |
| Call Price | =S*EXP(-q*T)*NORM.S.DIST(d1,TRUE)-K*EXP(-r*T)*NORM.S.DIST(d2,TRUE) | |
| Put Price | =K*EXP(-r*T)*NORM.S.DIST(-d2,TRUE)-S*EXP(-q*T)*NORM.S.DIST(-d1,TRUE) | |

### Greeks
| Greek | Call | Put |
|-------|------|-----|
| Delta | =EXP(-q*T)*NORM.S.DIST(d1,TRUE) | =EXP(-q*T)*(NORM.S.DIST(d1,TRUE)-1) |
| Gamma | =EXP(-q*T)*NORM.DIST(d1,0,1,FALSE)/(S*σ*SQRT(T)) | Same as Call |
